# {{.ProjectName}}

A web application built with JAWT.

## Getting Started

1. **Start development server**:
   ```bash
	jawt run
	```

2. **Build for production**:
   ```bash
	jawt build
	```

## Project Structure

```
	{{.ProjectName}}/
	├── app/                  # Application pages
	│   └── index.jml        # Home page
	├── components/          # Reusable components
	│   └── layout.jml      # Layout component
	├── scripts/            # TypeScript functionality
	│   └── main.ts         # Main script
	├── assets/             # Static assets
	│   ├── images/
	├── public/             # Public files
	├── jawt.project.json   # Project configuration
	├── tsconfig.json       # TypeScript configuration
	└── tailwind.config.js  # Tailwind CSS configuration
	```

## Available Commands

- `jawt run` - Start development server with hot reload
- `jawt build` - Build for production
- `jawt debug` - Build with debugging information

